Dialogue: 0,00:33:06.760,00:33:09.760,辉英,,0,0,0,,All you have to do is evaluate those integrals
Dialogue: 0,00:33:09.760,00:33:13.760,辉英,,0,0,0,,and use them and send it in Fmincon.
Dialogue: 0,00:33:13.760,00:33:17.760,辉英,,0,0,0,,See if you can come up with points and weights for it.
Dialogue: 0,00:33:17.760,00:33:21.760,辉英,,0,0,0,,This is going to have trouble.
Dialogue: 0,00:33:21.760,00:33:25.760,辉英,,0,0,0,,To do it this way, to set up the nonlinear system of equations,
Dialogue: 0,00:33:25.760,00:33:30.760,辉英,,0,0,0,,so we can write this nonlinear system in a kind of geometric way
Dialogue: 0,00:33:30.760,00:33:32.760,辉英,,0,0,0,,that helps us understand what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,00:33:32.760,00:33:37.760,辉英,,0,0,0,,We can write it as a matrix of whose columns are these evaluation points
Dialogue: 0,00:33:37.760,00:33:41.760,辉英,,0,0,0,,for all the different points.
