Dialogue: 0,00:33:47.760,00:33:49.760,辉英,,0,0,0,,the x to the l.
Dialogue: 0,00:33:49.760,00:33:54.760,辉英,,0,0,0,,So this last row corresponds to dealing with the x to the l polynomial,
Dialogue: 0,00:33:54.760,00:33:57.760,辉英,,0,0,0,,and the first row is the constant polynomial.
Dialogue: 0,00:33:57.760,00:34:00.760,辉英,,0,0,0,,And if you look at that system of equations,
Dialogue: 0,00:34:00.760,00:34:03.760,辉英,,0,0,0,,you should be able to see something almost immediately.
