Dialogue: 0,00:34:06.760,00:34:07.760,辉英,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,00:34:07.760,00:34:09.760,辉英,,0,0,0,,One of those rows is looking at a polynomial.
Dialogue: 0,00:34:09.760,00:34:11.760,辉英,,0,0,0,,So this is x1 through xn.
Dialogue: 0,00:34:11.760,00:34:14.760,辉英,,0,0,0,,These are points between the integrals 0 to 1.
Dialogue: 0,00:34:14.760,00:34:18.760,辉英,,0,0,0,,And the last row is taking each of those points to the lth power.
